{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act14side", "eventName": "風雪過境", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BI-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "獵場", "storyInfo": "博士透過雅兒瞭解了部分謝拉格的歷史。\n聖獵中，恩雅正與阿克托斯交談，突然一群野獸襲來，恩雅不僅不懼，反而出手折服眾人。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "人的領袖在耶拉岡德面前跪下，向祂獻上最高的敬意。然後詢問：", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“這片土地不再是無主之地。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“這片土地上的每一個人都崇拜您，敬仰您，您是我們所有人的領袖。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“所以，請告訴我們，我們的名字是什麼？”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "耶拉岡德回答：", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我已為你們想好名字。從今天起，這片土地就叫作謝拉格。而你們，就是謝拉格人。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": " ——《耶拉岡德》第二頁", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g12_mountpath", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "............", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿克托斯大人。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！我在，聖女大人有何吩咐？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#4$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必如此緊張，阿克托斯大人，我並非食人猛獸。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管怎麼說，這是您第一次親自參與聖獵。不光是我，您看看這些戰士們，在聖女大人您面前大家都繃緊了，想好好表現一番！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#3$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......作為聖女，與耶拉岡德的戰士們一同參與聖獵，我認為這是我應當做的。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您這話說得有理！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#3$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不說我了。我見您從狩獵開始時，就一直像是有什麼心事，若是有什麼想問的，就請直接問吧。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哈哈，瞞不過聖女大人，您見笑了。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#3$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若您不介意，可以將我當成一個朋友。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，我也會將您當成一個朋友。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人......", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我心中，也把聖女大人您當作一個朋友。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，就讓我們像朋友似的說話。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了，那麼恕我直言。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想知道，聖女大人，究竟是怎麼看待還政一事的？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您很爽快。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "朋友之間，自當如此。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我佩爾羅契家的人論戰鬥，不會輸給布朗陶和希瓦艾什，但論陰謀詭計，實在不是這兩家的對手。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彎彎繞繞，遮遮掩掩絕非我的風格。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說得不錯......", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我的朋友，還是得請您原諒我。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在回答您的問題之前，我需要先向您確認一件事。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人請說。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿克托斯大人，您是一位忠勇、虔誠的戰士。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我清楚您率直、爽快，同時我也知曉，您絕不是真的毫無考慮。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然您說朋友之間理應不遮不掩，那麼我亦當效仿。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——我想知道，一直以來，為什麼您會如此堅定地反對恩希歐迪斯的開放政策？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我是個粗人，聖女大人。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論恩希歐迪斯將他的所謂開放吹得有多好，有多吸引人，我要的不是那些誇誇其談，不是那些漂亮話。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只看他帶來了什麼。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我看到的是湧進我們家中的毫無信仰的外國人，是打著發展旗號對土地山川的破壞，是在他的領地裡工作後日漸失去信仰的謝拉格人。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他帶進來的那些東西是好用，他因此賺了很多錢，造了很多大房子，我當然知道。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是如果人人都學他那樣，為了所謂的發展，就把信仰拋在腦後，那麼這片土地會變成什麼樣子？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德既然令我佩爾羅契家守衛謝拉格，那我阿克托斯就決不能容忍有任何人，以任何方式想要將其破壞！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......阿克托斯大人的想法我明白了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼該我回答您的問題了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯大人提出要將核心領地盡數交於我手，此事事出突然，確實在我的意料之外。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人果然也不知情嗎？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實，在此之前，我對他竟有這種打算一無所知。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是——", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論恩希歐迪斯大人究竟是出於何種考量，才提出還政一事，就結果而言，我並不認為這是一個很壞的發展。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的意思是......", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我坐在蔓珠院中，日日夜夜看著人們向耶拉岡德祈禱。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一點我比恩希歐迪斯大人要清楚，那就是——謝拉格還無法失去信仰。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既做出了這樣的決定，接下來的許多事情，我想，就不再是誰個人說了便能算數的了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "意外總會發生，不是嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若恩希歐迪斯大人沒有提前料想到這一點，那就是他的不是了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......行，其他的我不管，但我信您這句話。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實不相瞞，您剛剛說話時，直到聽到您最後的話之前，我都覺得自己好像不是在與聖女大人對話，而是在面對另一個人。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許這是我多心了。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果會讓阿克托斯大人產生這樣的感覺，我必須說，這讓我感到難過。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我絕不會否認，我也姓希瓦艾什。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，成為聖女後我的一切便與俗世割離。令這個姓氏於我而言不再有意義的，卻也正是恩希歐迪斯大人。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人......", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#6$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_monsterroar", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "野獸們終於按捺不住了嗎......", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人準備狩獵！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g6_square", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.8, "loop": "true", "channel": "bse"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人畫像，聖女大人刺繡，聖女大人雕像！", "name": "商人A"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格人的信仰象徵，還猶豫什麼，現在就將耶拉岡德的祝福請回家！", "name": "商人A"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "人真多......;......;Sharp那邊不知道順不順利。", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line156", "option2": "line156", "option3": "line156"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 157, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿！", "name": "雅兒"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "（發出難以名狀的叫聲）;你的手好冰！;（下意識地反擊）", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line164", "option2": "line167", "option3": "line170"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line173"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，反而嚇了我一跳......", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#3$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line173"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回過神來啦？", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#7$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "3"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line173"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚哇，你的手好冰啊......", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#4$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發什麼呆呢，我一眼就看到你站在這兒一動不動的。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，該不會真的嚇到你了？", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#3$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "還好。;......;嚇死我了！", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line181", "option2": "line181", "option3": "line181"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，你這不是根本沒事嘛！", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛你在看什麼？之前的聖獵儀式你看到了沒？這次就連聖女大人也要一起參加狩獵，大家都很期待呢！", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "大典的由來是怎樣的？;你看起來興致不是很高。;有什麼推薦的娛樂項目嗎？", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line188", "option2": "line195", "option3": "line204"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line209"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據說是因為蔓珠院幾百年前從古籍中發現耶拉岡德初現的日子是這天，於是就把這天定為了謝拉格最大的節日。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於大典要做什麼......", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如你所見，對普通人來說，就是享受節日的歡愉。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對聖女大人來說，則還有一項工作要做——為聖獵獲得的山雪鬼戰利品驅魔。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "具體是怎麼樣的過程，你等一下就能看到了。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line209"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，有沒有人說過你真的很敏銳......", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然每到這種時候，我就可以拋下院裡的事務，出來享受節日。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過一想到聖女大人還有那麼多事要做，而那些事我又都幫不上忙，心裡還是有些不是滋味......", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#6$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且......", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#6$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，算了，大過節的，不說這些了。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "3"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line209"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，這你可就問對人了。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娛樂項目......可能沒有多少，畢竟除了集市之外，大多還是和耶拉岡德有關的東西。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，如果你想借此瞭解耶拉岡德的話，這可是個好機會。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走，我帶你到處逛逛~", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每年到這個時候，於大學院任教和學習的修士們會來到蔓珠院中，在這裡為人們講經，或者講述有關耶拉岡德的歷史。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_268"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "千年前，祖先們觸怒了耶拉岡德，耶拉岡德不再保護謝拉格，嚴冬就此降臨。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了平息耶拉岡德的怒火，蔓珠院每年都會挑選靈魂最為純潔的少女，踏上天路，將代表祂的鈴鐺掛上山巔，並將自己的靈魂獻給祂。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在第一百位少女的呼喚下，耶拉岡德終於寬恕了謝拉格的人民，嚴冬終於終結。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而謝拉格的第一任聖女也正是由此誕生。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是這一段歷史啊......對了，我在蔓珠院的典籍中，還看過另一個版本的故事。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "另一個版本？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line237"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "為了平息耶拉岡德的怒火，謝拉格每年都會選出一名少女作為聖女，前往喀蘭峰頂，靜坐祈禱至死。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "因為傳說耶拉岡德過去也是以少女的姿態出現在人們面前，人們相信，少女純潔的靈魂能夠抵達祂的身邊，然後喚回祂。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在這個儀式持續了將近百年以後，逐漸有人開始無法忍受這種得不到回報的儀式。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在一個女兒被選為聖女的小家族族長的帶領下，一次針對蔓珠院的反抗發生了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這次反抗的結果是，蔓珠院的許多建築毀於一旦，眾多遠古時期留下的卷宗都在這場反抗中被毀壞。從此，蔓珠院自身對於過去的瞭解出現了極大斷層。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "而戲劇性的是，這一年，聖女還是登上了喀蘭峰頂，而耶拉岡德的力量也在數百年的沉眠中得到了恢復。在聖女的祈禱下，祂甦醒了過來。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "祂甦醒的預兆是那麼明顯，以至於謝拉格人民立刻就感知到了。對蔓珠院的反抗剛進行到一半，就以這種方式被終結了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "聽起來更有現實感。;聽起來像是你親眼所見。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line253", "option2": "line256"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line259"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是吧，同時也很殘忍。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#4$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line259"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有沒有。我在經卷閣裡偶然發現的，可能是當時的親歷者留下的記錄，也有可能只是單純的妄言。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 260, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_250_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，謝拉格的雪山，是會吃人的。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#4$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g12_mountpath", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#6$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爺！前方突然出現大批野獸......！", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#6$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些野獸異常暴躁，正在攻擊我們最前方的戰士！", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#6$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "區區野獸，不足為懼！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們留在這裡保護聖女大人，保持陣型不要慌亂。瓦萊絲，你也留下。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他人跟我來，支援前方的兄弟們！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿克托斯大人，請等一等！", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也與各位一起。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，聖女大人的安全......", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#2$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瓦萊絲說得對，聖女大人的安全最重要，您放心在這裡等著便是，我佩爾羅契家的勇士們必定護聖女大人您周全！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "慢著，阿克托斯！", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......菈塔托絲？你怎麼會在這，你們另兩家的人不是該分頭往兩翼行動嗎？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#4$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希瓦艾什已經出發了。但我總覺得有什麼地方不對勁，本想分隊前過來提醒你要小心......現在看來倒是沒這個必要了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這話什麼意思？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔托絲大人是想說，前方出現的獸群不同尋常？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人聰慧。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然還不知道具體情況......但我總有不太好的預感。但願不要又是有什麼人，光作秀嫌不夠，還要在聖獵這樣莊嚴的場合作怪就好。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之小心點總沒錯。這次聖獵......連聖女大人都親自蒞臨，總歸是不同以往的。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔托絲大人言重了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過您說的話也不無道理，我既已在此，便是要與各位勇士站在一處，沒有對危機避而不見的道理。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩位，情況緊急，邊走邊說吧。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人能如此想，是謝拉格之幸！再阻攔就是我的不是了，瓦萊絲，你帶路，我們走！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是！", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#5$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowcrwdmarch", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（怎麼還不出現啊，莫希......！聖女參與聖獵這種千載難逢的好事都遇上了，在聖女面前解決野獸，多好的機會！）", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（但萬一......萬一傷到聖女......）", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......啊呀不管了，菈塔托絲那女人總不會真把我怎麼樣！大不了我扛著就是了......）", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（一定要抓住機會啊，莫希！）", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g13_mountpath_s", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warchaos_intro", "key": "$warchaos_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_monsterroar", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sing