acter", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些野獸怎麼不知道怕？！", "name": "年長的謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種情況絕不正常......", "name": "年長的謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為這次有聖女在隊伍裡，這些山裡的野獸也會多畏懼幾分。", "name": "年輕的謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來也不儘然，聖女也沒那麼大的面子啊......", "name": "年輕的謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞎說什麼！聖女大人也是你能隨便談論的？！", "name": "年長的謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這話要是被阿克托斯大人聽到了，你自己好好想想後果！", "name": "年長的謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了好了，我知道了！哪敢被阿克托斯大人聽到，肯定要被罵死了......", "name": "年輕的謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_singleblunt", "volume": 3.0}}, {"id": 